quran[6{c,v,t}:
5,90,"ae logo jo imaan laaye ho, yeh sharaab aur juaa aur yeh astane aur panse, yeh sab ganday shaytani kaam hain, un se parhaiz karo, umeed hai ke tumhe Falah naseeb hogi"
5,91,shetan to yeh chahta hai ke sharaab aur juye ke zareya se tumahray darmain adawat aur bughz daal day aur tumhe khuda ki yaad se aur namaz se rok day phir kya tum un cheezon se baz raho ge ?
5,92,"Allah aur uss ke rasool ki baat manu aur baz aa jao, lekin agar tum ne hukum aduli ki to jaan lau ke hamaray rasool par bas saaf saaf hukum pouncha dainay ki zimma daari thi"
5,93,"jo log imaan le aeye aur naik amal karne lagey unhon ne pehlay jo kuch khaya piya tha is par koi girift nah hogi bashart e kay woh aindah unn cheezon se bachay rahen jo haraam ki gayi hain aur imaan par saabit qadam rahen aur achay kaam karen, phir jis jis cheez se roka jaye is se rkin aur jo farmaan Ellahi ho ussay manen, phir khuda tarsi ke sath naik rawayya rakhen Allah naik kirdaar logon ko pasand karta hai"
5,94,"ae logo jo imaan laaye ho, Allah tumhe uss shikaar ke zareya se sakht azmaish mein daaley ga jo bilkul tumahray hathon aur nizon ki zad mein hoga, yeh dekhnay ke liye ke tum mein se kon is se ghayebana darta hai, phir jis ne is tanbeeh ke baad Allah ki muqarrar ki hui hadd se tajawaz kya uss ke liye dard naak saza hai"
5,95,"ae logo jo imaan laaye ho! ahraam ki haalat mein shikaar nah maro, aur agar tum mein se koi jaan boojh kar aisa kar guzray to jo janwar is ne mara ho usi ke hum palla aik janwar ussay maweshion mein se Nazar dena hoga jis ka faisla tum mein se do adil aadmi karen ge, aur yeh nazrana kaaba pohanchaya jaye ga, ya nahi to iss gunah ke kaffara mein chand miskeeno ko khana khilana hoga, yaas ke baqadar rozay rakhnay hon ge, taakay woh apne kiye ka maza chakhay pehlay jo ho chuka ussay Allah ne maaf kar diya, lekin ab agar kisi ne is harkat ka iada kya to is se Allah badla le ga, Allah sab par ghalib hai aur badla lainay ki taaqat rakhta hai"
